    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199740/extras/8d88b028d7a66d81d5024e417185b924.poster.avif?t=1741334410\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199740/extras/8d88b028d7a66d81d5024e417185b924.webm?t=1741334410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199740/extras/8d88b028d7a66d81d5024e417185b924.mp4?t=1741334410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong><br>DEFEAT OPPONENTS FROM MULTIPLE DIMENSIONS OR PERISH TRYING</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have been chosen for a dangerous mission—many have fallen before you. Will you have the determination to complete it? We are counting on you.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore Diverse Dimensions</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each opponent has their own unique dimension. Will you be able to visit them all?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Combat System</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight with a sword, block enemy attacks, or dodge them! Don't forget about healing, either. The combat system is inspired by Soulslike games but played from a first-person perspective.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Try to Survive Until the End</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face five challenging opponents, each with unique abilities. You'll have to learn their attack patterns and find their weaknesses to emerge victorious. If you die, you'll have to start your journey from the beginning...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Speedrun Mode</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try to complete the game as quickly as possible with the built-in time-tracking system. Of course, this is entirely optional.</p>",
